---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Architecture — Gen_Agent">
  <section class="page">
    <h1>Architecture</h1>
    <p>Modular Python stack: simulation engine, memory system, personality, and web API.</p>
    <pre class="diagram">SimEngine → ProximityDetector → Dialogues → MemoryManager
MemoryManager → models / storage / decay
Stanford submodule → plan_to_poi</pre>
    <ul>
      <li><code>core/sim/</code> — tick engine, pathfinding, events</li>
      <li><code>core/memory/</code> — universal memory, SQLite, decay</li>
      <li><code>server/</code> + <code>web/</code> — FastAPI and UI</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
